00:00:06.640 --> 00:00:09.920
Biography of Emil Fischbacher, Missionary
to China

cue-3
00:00:11.600 --> 00:00:12.680
by Marshall Broomhall.

cue-4
00:00:14.100 --> 00:00:18.360
Mark fourteen, verse four: "To what
purpose has this waste of ointment been

cue-5
00:00:18.360 --> 00:00:18.680
made?"

